title: If you offer suggestions to the service, they become the owner of the ideas that you give them
quoteText: By submitting ideas, suggestions, documents, and/or proposals (“Submissions”) to Bigo or Likee Services or its employees, you acknowledge and agree that Bigo or Likee Services shall be entitled to use or disclose such Submissions for any purpose in any way without providing compensation or credit to you.
